What's up?

1414
00:43:37,088 --> 00:43:37,720
Are you cold?

1415
00:43:39,480 --> 00:43:40,160
Are you cold?

1416
00:43:40,160 --> 00:43:41,200
No, I have this.

1417
00:43:41,200 --> 00:43:42,160
