No.

1419
00:43:45,440 --> 00:43:46,144
Say you're cold.

1420
00:43:49,856 --> 00:43:51,040
What shoes are you wearing?

1421
00:43:51,600 --> 00:43:51,920
Slippers.

1422
00:43:51,920 --> 00:43:52,840
Oh, slippers.

1423
00:43:53,720 --> 00:43:54,816
I changed into slippers
right when I got back.

1424
00:43:56,320 --> 00:43:57,280
Actually, instead of sitting here,

1425
00:43:57,280 --> 00:43:58,240
