1427
00:44:00,000 --> 00:44:00,680
He's clever.

1428
00:44:00,680 --> 00:44:01,920
He asked her to go out.

1429
00:44:01,920 --> 00:44:02,752
Just a little stroll.

1430
00:44:02,752 --> 00:44:04,200
