1436
00:44:09,160 --> 00:44:10,432
Then I'll go change.

1437
00:44:10,520 --> 00:44:11,080
Go ahead.

1438
00:44:11,080 --> 00:44:11,800
Do you want to change shoes?

1439
00:44:12,320 --> 00:44:14,240
Can you put down the big blanket?

1440
00:44:26,624 --> 00:44:27,480
(Dropped the giant blanket)

1441
00:44:27,480 --> 00:44:29,472
She won't go out wearing
a heavy coat, right?

1442
00:44:29,984 --> 00:44:32,640
(Make an appearance!)

1443
00:44:32,640 --> 00:44:33,760
Are you heading out at the same time?

1444
00:44:35,320 --> 00:44:36,520
(Not getting cold at all)
I knew it.

1445
00:44:36,520 --> 00:44:37,880
(Really bundled up.)

1446
00:44:41,520 --> 00:44:42,656
The moment I looked at her,

1447
00:44:42,880 --> 00:44:44,400
