1448
00:44:44,400 --> 00:44:45,480
(Inner layer: heat-locking sweater)
and a coat on top.

1449
00:44:45,480 --> 00:44:47,840
(Outer layer: windproof jacket)
How could I possibly lend her more?

1450
00:44:48,440 --> 00:44:49,600
I kept thinking

1451
00:44:50,880 --> 00:44:52,800
can this wind please get stronger?

1452
00:44:52,800 --> 00:44:53,680
But there's a problem.

1453
00:44:53,680 --> 00:44:54,560
If it gets stronger,

1454
00:44:54,560 --> 00:44:55,920
