This is too hard.

1456
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:01,024
(Manifesting)
This task is impossible now.

1457
00:45:02,120 --> 00:45:03,320
(I need to find the right timing)

1458
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:04,640
(to drape this jacket on her.)

1459
00:45:04,920 --> 00:45:06,760
Here comes your wind.

1460
00:45:07,920 --> 00:45:09,440
That day I didn't ask you out,

1461
00:45:09,440 --> 00:45:10,320
did it bother you?

1462
00:45:11,520 --> 00:45:12,736
Finally discussing this issue.

1463
00:45:13,480 --> 00:45:14,680
I've been actually thinking about this.

1464
00:45:15,840 --> 00:45:16,520
Like what?

1465
00:45:16,520 --> 00:45:17,664
I've been actually thinking about this.

1466
00:45:17,840 --> 00:45:18,560
About what?

1467
00:45:19,320 --> 00:45:21,120
I kind of guessed

1468
00:45:21,240 --> 00:45:22,480
that Chen Jianying

1469
00:45:22,480 --> 00:45:23,760
would ask me out.

1470
00:45:24,640 --> 00:45:25,120
You guessed

1471
00:45:25,120 --> 00:45:26,368
that Chen Jianying would invite you?

1472
00:45:26,560 --> 00:45:27,680
I figured it out.

1473
00:45:27,680 --> 00:45:28,800
I had a hunch.

1474
00:45:29,240 --> 00:45:31,480
I could definitely sense some things.

1475
00:45:36,920 --> 00:45:38,040
So then I...

1476
00:45:38,040 --> 00:45:39,072
I thought, well...

1477
00:45:39,360 --> 00:45:40,120
Actually, I thought,

1478
00:45:40,120 --> 00:45:41,960
