1479
00:45:42,440 --> 00:45:43,080
Later, I found out.

1480
00:45:44,520 --> 00:45:45,440
Actually, I felt okay about it.

1481
00:45:45,440 --> 00:45:47,240
I didn't find it weird.

1482
00:45:47,640 --> 00:45:49,720
I don't care.

1483
00:45:52,320 --> 00:45:52,960
So?

1484
00:45:52,960 --> 00:45:54,160
Why didn't you invite me?

1485
00:45:54,784 --> 00:45:55,960
(Not weird, just curious)

1486
00:45:55,960 --> 00:45:57,240
I just wanted you

1487
00:45:57,880 --> 00:46:00,192
