1488
00:46:09,440 --> 00:46:10,000
Are you cold?

1489
00:46:10,600 --> 00:46:11,680
I'm okay. I'm dressed warmly.

1490
00:46:11,680 --> 00:46:12,120
Are you cold?

1491
00:46:12,120 --> 00:46:12,800
I'm alright.

1492
00:46:13,960 --> 00:46:15,080
I have two layers on.

1493
00:46:15,560 --> 00:46:16,400
A sweater inside.

1494
00:46:16,400 --> 00:46:17,320
A windbreaker outside.

1495
00:46:18,825 --> 00:46:19,360
(Just laughing it off)

1496
00:46:19,360 --> 00:46:20,608
Stop asking.

1497
00:46:20,864 --> 00:46:21,320
Just stop asking

1498
00:46:21,320 --> 00:46:22,272
