1499
00:46:22,440 --> 00:46:23,760
Shall we head back?

1500
00:46:23,760 --> 00:46:24,200
Sure.

1501
00:46:25,200 --> 00:46:27,120
When I passed by
the first floor of the house earlier,

1502
00:46:27,120 --> 00:46:27,968
