1503
00:46:27,968 --> 00:46:28,680
All downstairs.

1504
00:46:28,680 --> 00:46:30,040
No one could go back to their rooms.

1505
00:46:30,144 --> 00:46:32,064
(Clarification: No such rule.)

1506
00:46:34,880 --> 00:46:35,720
Did yours go off too?

1507
00:46:35,720 --> 00:46:36,280
Mine didn't.

1508
00:46:36,840 --> 00:46:37,960
