1537
00:47:20,200 --> 00:47:20,864
Indeed.

1538
00:47:21,160 --> 00:47:22,640
Well then, let's go, us two.

1539
00:47:26,240 --> 00:47:27,120
That's good.

1540
00:47:27,120 --> 00:47:28,000
So pretty.

1541
00:47:28,512 --> 00:47:29,400
(Forcing in)
Looking good.

1542
00:47:33,024 --> 00:47:33,440
(Zhou Youling's photo partner)

1543
00:47:33,440 --> 00:47:33,952
(Chen Jianying, Wang Yi,
Xu Lvyang, Chen Danqi)

1544
00:47:33,952 --> 00:47:36,480
(Completed the task multiple times)

1545
00:47:36,480 --> 00:47:38,208
(He took photos with them all)

1546
00:47:38,528 --> 00:47:39,616
(Freezing here)

1547
00:47:40,280 --> 00:47:41,560
