1552
00:47:50,000 --> 00:47:50,360
No.

1553
00:47:50,360 --> 00:47:51,920
I just played briefly yesterday.

1554
00:47:52,560 --> 00:47:53,360
Awkward conversation.

1555
00:47:53,880 --> 00:47:55,320
Because I kept thinking

1556
00:47:55,320 --> 00:47:56,560
(Air-tight)
when's the best time

1557
00:47:56,560 --> 00:47:57,952
