1582
00:48:47,680 --> 00:48:49,760
What's Dong Zhuoran's task now?

1583
00:48:50,048 --> 00:48:51,680
(I couldn't decide who
to invite at that time.)

1584
00:48:52,256 --> 00:48:55,552
(Dong Zhuoran plans to invite: TBD)

1585
00:48:57,440 --> 00:48:58,880
I was thinking

1586
