because of this.

1612
00:49:31,600 --> 00:49:32,280
Thank you.

1613
00:49:32,672 --> 00:49:35,120
(Xiao Wentao,
Task completed successfully)

1614
00:49:35,120 --> 00:49:36,400
It wasn't that hard.

1615
00:49:36,880 --> 00:49:38,624
