1616
00:49:39,616 --> 00:49:40,480
(But I got to ask her out.)

1617
00:49:40,480 --> 00:49:41,440
(I was very happy.)

1618
00:49:41,920 --> 00:49:43,080
Alright, let's head back now.

1619
00:49:43,080 --> 00:49:43,808
I think the wind's a bit too strong.

1620
00:49:44,040 --> 00:49:44,608
