1640
00:50:23,600 --> 00:50:24,736
RT and BK.

1641
00:50:25,160 --> 00:50:26,440
(The day before)
So gifted.

1642
00:50:27,280 --> 00:50:29,200
You're the best student I've trained.

1643
00:50:29,200 --> 00:50:30,000
How great?

1644
00:50:30,000 --> 00:50:30,624
Just perfect.

1645
00:50:31,136 --> 00:50:31,648
Let's go.

1646
00:50:39,120 --> 00:50:40,040
Only her room.

1647
00:50:40,040 --> 00:50:41,400
