to see it as just a gift.

1656
00:51:12,686 --> 00:51:13,446
He is here.

1657
00:51:13,958 --> 00:51:14,438
He is coming.

1658
00:51:14,646 --> 00:51:15,246
He is coming.

1659
00:51:15,646 --> 00:51:16,686
